g.text: Turn on current supply to antenna burnwire mechanism for 1 minute
Record deployment time to event log
Listen for ground station command for next 2 minutes
Record impedence probe data to event log for next 2 minutes at 1 second intervals
Turn on current supply to DeCs burnwire mechanism for 1 minute
Record DeCS strain gauge data to event log for next 2 minutes at 1 second intervals
Record multi-spectral sensor data to event log for next 2 minutes at 1 second intervals
